Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Ethics Bias Detection Module Stub
Provides comprehensive bias detection and analysis capabilities for AI systems
Enables statistical bias detection, causal bias analysis, and intersectional bias assessment
:End Note

Type BiasDetectionSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    detection_methods as List[BiasDetectionMethod]
    bias_metrics as List[BiasMetric]
    detection_algorithms as List[BiasDetectionAlgorithm]
    bias_assessment_framework as BiasAssessmentFramework
    bias_reporting_system as BiasReportingSystem
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type BiasDetectionMethod is Dictionary with:
    method_id as String
    method_name as String
    method_type as String
    applicable_bias_types as List[String]
    method_parameters as MethodParameters
    detection_accuracy as Float
    computational_complexity as Float
    method_limitations as List[String]

Type BiasMetric is Dictionary with:
    metric_id as String
    metric_name as String
    metric_type as String
    metric_formula as String
    metric_interpretation as String
    metric_thresholds as Dictionary
    metric_validation as MetricValidation

Type BiasDetectionAlgorithm is Dictionary with:
    algorithm_id as String
    algorithm_name as String
    algorithm_type as String
    algorithm_parameters as AlgorithmParameters
    algorithm_performance as AlgorithmPerformance
    algorithm_limitations as List[String]

Type BiasAssessmentFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    assessment_criteria as List[AssessmentCriterion]
    assessment_methodologies as List[AssessmentMethodology]
    assessment_metrics as List[AssessmentMetric]
    assessment_reporting as AssessmentReporting

Type BiasReportingSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    reporting_templates as List[ReportingTemplate]
    reporting_formats as List[ReportingFormat]
    reporting_frequency as String
    reporting_automation as ReportingAutomation

Type DetectionContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    data_context as Dictionary
    model_context as Dictionary
    bias_requirements as Dictionary
    detection_constraints as Dictionary
    context_metadata as Dictionary

Type BiasContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    bias_analysis_scope as Dictionary
    bias_detection_parameters as Dictionary
    bias_assessment_criteria as Dictionary
    bias_metadata as Dictionary

Type CausalContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    causal_analysis_requirements as Dictionary
    causal_model_parameters as Dictionary
    causal_inference_constraints as Dictionary
    causal_metadata as Dictionary

Type IntersectionalContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    intersectional_analysis_scope as Dictionary
    intersectional_parameters as Dictionary
    intersectional_constraints as Dictionary
    intersectional_metadata as Dictionary

Type AssessmentResult is Dictionary with:
    result_id as String
    bias_assessment as Dictionary
    bias_metrics as Dictionary
    bias_recommendations as List[String]
    assessment_confidence as Float
    result_metadata as Dictionary

Type MonitoringContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    monitoring_requirements as Dictionary
    monitoring_frequency as String
    monitoring_parameters as Dictionary
    monitoring_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "create_bias_detection_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "detect_comprehensive_bias" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and detection_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "detect_statistical_bias" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "detect_representation_bias" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "detect_measurement_bias" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "detect_algorithmic_bias" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_causal_bias_analysis" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "detect_intersectional_bias" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "synthesize_bias_assessment" that takes detection_result as Dictionary and bias_detection_system as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "monitor_bias_over_time" that takes bias_detection_system as Dictionary and monitoring_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_bias_detection_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_bias_detection_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 